          "type": "richtext",
          "id": "answer",
          "label": "Answer",
          "default": "<p>Yes, absolutely. We use only 100% Grade 6A Mulberry Silk, 22 momme thickness. It is the highest grade available, ensuring durability and the ultimate smooth feel.</p>"
